  botName: Kroonoko
  description: Kroonoko is a Kokonotian native to the Pogoo Archipelago. As a child
    he always loved ArcherHex, to the point that he convinced his parents to bring
    him to watch the Kaamanian planetary championships in person. While in Kaaman
    he trained with some of the best ArrowHex players in the world. Although he mostly
    lost matches, he became the undisputed planetary champion when he returned to
    his home planet.
